summary:
I finally went to see Captain Marvel before Endgame comes out and OH MY GOD I LOVE CAROL DANVERS SO MUCH
There are so many...
body:
I finally went to see Captain Marvel before Endgame comes out and OH MY GOD I LOVE CAROL DANVERS SO MUCH

There are so many reasons I loved the movie, when No Doubt played in that one scene I teared up because I realised that young girls are going to see that and feel so bloody powerful. As someone who constantly felt like I could never match up to all the boys growing up, I’m so happy that this is here for girls because it’s what I wanted back then.

And in addition to that, Carol Danvers could kick me in the throat and I would thank her because I have a massive crush on her
